      "content": "This design covers the RFC 9002 recovery slice, including ACK processing, transport-parameter inputs, timer behavior, and the recovery contracts that sit on top of the transport layer.\nIt does not duplicate RFC 9000 transport framing or RFC 9001 TLS packet-protection behavior."
